content: What happens if you say "Beetlejuice" three times?

If I say "Beetlejuice" three times, nothing specific happens because I am an artificial intelligence language model and do not have any connection to the supernatural or any specific references. However, in the context of the movie "Beetlejuice," saying his name three times can summon him. But again, that's just within the fictional universe of the movie. In reality, nothing will happen if you say "Beetlejuice" three times.
